            "weighted_score": 0.5615290403366089,
            "steam_purchase": true,
            "review_text": "If you want to play a Naruto 3d fighter, this game sure is one. Looks very good and all that, some frame drops during boss battles that I really feel my pc shouldn't have?\n\nI still think the first Storm game is the most fun one in general (both the battle gameplay and the silly little story mode where you walk around the village are great), but this has a lot more character variety if you're going for that."
