        {
            "review_id": "226594087",
            "steam_id": "76561198769119080",
            "playtime_minutes": 17,
            "voted_up": true,
            "votes_up": 1,
            "weighted_score": 0.52173912525177,
            "steam_purchase": true,
            "review_text": "Best game naruto. I can play pvp split screen with bro. Base game until final battle naruto vs sasuke. After that unlock 'The Last' character (naruto, sasuke, sakura, hinata & hanabi). I purchased 1dlc '4 sound ninja' BUT refund it after play few times, after update all my UNLOCK CHARACTER N STORY PROGRESS got ERASED. I need to play again from beginning....but its ok."
        },
        {
            "review_id": "226414562",
            "steam_id": "76561198056276191",
            "playtime_minutes": 1226,
            "voted_up": true,
            "votes_up": 1,
            "weighted_score": 0.52173912525177,
            "steam_purchase": true,
            "review_text": "The last decent storm game in the series in my opinion. Beefy roster, smooth mechanics. I hop back in every now and then just to relive the experience. It covers the end of the Naruto saga, but there's plenty to keep you busy."
        },
        {
            "review_id": "226081341",
            "steam_id": "76561198706596555",
            "playtime_minutes": 574,
            "voted_up": true,
            "votes_up": 1,
            "weighted_score": 0.52173912525177,
            "steam_purchase": true,
            "review_text": "I enjoyed the gameplay and the story mode it foloowed the actual story of Naruto Shippuden, One thing I did not like was that there was no training on controls what so ever at the beginning of the game you have to find the training yourself in the menu"
        },
        {
            "review_id": "225798435",
            "steam_id": "76561198131577950",
            "playtime_minutes": 2994,
            "voted_up": true,
            "votes_up": 2,
            "weighted_score": 0.5167785286903381,
            "steam_purchase": true,
            "review_text": "One of the best games ever made, and the only game where I’ve unlocked 100% of all achievements twice. 🏆\nI originally got the Platinum trophy back on PS4, and just did it all over again here! \nI think that speaks for itself! 😎\n\nThe combat system is absolutely insane! 🔥\n\nA must-play title for every Naruto fan! 🍥"
        },
        {
            "review_id": "227454255",
            "steam_id": "76561198360048137",
            "playtime_minutes": 2510,
            "voted_up": true,
            "votes_up": 0,
            "weighted_score": 0.5,
            "steam_purchase": true,
            "review_text": "The Ultimate Ninja Storm series has always seemed to me the best approach to the Naruto story. This game does not dissapoint with the ending\r\n\r\nIt completely cuts out third's world exploration in story mode, and everything ends up being a battle selector—but what battles!\r\n\r\nIt's impressive, but knowing how these kinds of games are, it's hard to imagine them changing much from one to the next. However, having played through all the previous ones, UNS4 touches on a thousand things, making it the most enjoyable game in the franchise so far.\r\n\r\nThe DLC is kinda mid imo.\r\n\r\nI recommend it, but if by the time you read this there's already a game that has the entire Naruto story in a single title, don't hesitate to jump straight to that one."
        },
        {
            "review_id": "225565181",
            "steam_id": "76561198055705638",
            "playtime_minutes": 3630,
            "voted_up": false,
            "votes_up": 1,
            "weighted_score": 0.4834437072277069,
            "steam_purchase": true,
            "review_text": "Awesome Game, and awesome story, but online is a straight up mess. A lot of players have really high ping or lag switch, and there is no anti-cheat engine. Every now and then you can have a legit match, but most the matches are rigged by cheaters who lag switch, and activate high ping so that you can't even block or react to there hits at all. I am straight up pro at this game so it's kind of sad to see the online status of this game full of high ping players, cheaters, and straight up lag switchers, I straight up got recordings of people lag switching like catching them in the act and stuff, and one time a player apologized and begged me to not report them."
        },
