            "steam_purchase": true,
            "review_text": "The game looks stunning but is extremely disappointing as it is absolutely not adapted to the PC. Completety unplayable. Why sell it to the PC players if you don't even bother to adapt it to their game device??????????? What am I supposed to do with this A button which is not even A on the keyboard???????? Why so many B's in a combination for casting a single Ninjutsu??????? Also no way of changing the game display from a single window to a full screen. Even if you manage to set the keys on the keyboard with the help of tutorials on the Internet, you still can play with one hand only, the second one doesn't exist apparently. The creators must have been thinking I am Sasuke Uchiha with only one hand left after the 4th Ninja War or something. It's been years and noone bothered to adapt the game for PC.  Utter disappointment."
